reviews.review_text: One One of my very first tapes. Along with Springfield from 78. I fell in love with this band because of bootlegs and then seeing them live.  NEVER ENOUGH of either. Still 35 years later.  plus this is one hot show and very good recording.
Strong Top form here, some beautiful slide guitar.
